def find_best_sushi_restaurant(city):
    url = f'https://api.yelp.com/v3/businesses/search?term=sushi&location={city}'
    headers = {'Authorization': 'Bearer <YELP_API_KEY>'}
    response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
    data = response.json()
    best_restaurant = data['businesses'][0]
    return best_restaurant
